_sText:
Ok my first climb map.

It is an easy map for "Rookies".
Means not many huge jumps.
The map hast three levels.

Level 1 : Easy
Level 2 : Mid
Level 3 : Mid + Platforms you cam fall through.

-Fall damage is deactivated.
-At the end is a button to kill the other. [Just for fun :D]
-Scout can be used for better jumps.

So all together it is a training map.
